" /> 放低左咁耐希望仲可以學得好"},{"pid":"f66e19f50f3a8c719fa53a066278b252c14c8677","tid":396612,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做paper</blockquote><br />\nCambridge ielts books?<br />\n定我應該由最基本搞好啲grammar打好個底先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一邊做gramma 一邊做reading pp</blockquote><br />\n作文背範文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nlistening 易過ue 好多。。。 我ue listening f...其實最大原因係唔洗寫字咁, ue 要默書 ,ielts 就 mc.。 ue 好多時聽到又唔識串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者個answer 要全中先有分<br />\n<br />\n u grad 前考ilets.. listening 7.5 reading 7 writing 6 oral 5.5 之後overall 6.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26b137d5eb585e6898ccdb81aef3f812386ca2e","tid":396612,"uid":62079,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先學好grammar, 基本句式 e.g. subject, verb, object<br />\n<br />\n搞清楚tense既使用 , preposition既使用，呢啲係個英文底蘊嚟，真係唔知點入手就買本中學雞既grammar in use刨下，讀晒做晒應該都有咁上下進步<br />\n<br />\n每日都抽啲時間睇英文報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇下video新聞，初初先揀啲有興趣，識既報導睇，唔識既生字抄低，查<strong>英文字典</strong>，主要培養閲讀速度同豐富詞彙<br />\n<br />\n抄低左既字用黎作句，你識用返出黎先叫你識既野<br />\n<br />\n覺得睇大部分文章都冇乜問題既時候就做ielts paper, 再搵個補習老師執一執，有時俾錢係有用，因為佢睇到你既盲點(前題個老師要有料), 有心既半年要提升到正常程度其實唔難<br />\n<br />\n但要持之以恆，語言唔同skills，skills明左學左就一理通百理明，語言唔用好易忘記，因為已經過左最易入腦既黃金期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fba2c6f37fc44f4f710594f90ab89d450bb8e7e","tid":396612,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:52:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>GT 定academic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAcademic 啊巴打</blockquote><br />\n想讀書定移民呀<br />\n其實唔難丫 搞清楚基本野<br />\n有心學既好快考倒6.5啦"},{"pid":"f5a52faac